data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home located in the Waters Edge Community in the Stephenson High School District. The main level features a bright 2-story foyer, formal living room, formal dining room, half bath, fireside great room open to the beautiful and light kitchen with granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances! The upper level features the owner’s suite with an ensuite bathroom with separate sinks, whirlpool tub, separate shower and large walk-in closet. There are also 3 secondary bedrooms and a full bath on the upper level. There is a patio off the eat-in kitchen to the large and level backyard, perfect for pets, playtime and entertaining. Located in a resort style amenity community featuring a lake, clubhouse, pool, several tennis and pickleball courts, a volleyball court, basketball court and playground. Come check out this beautiful home and amazing community and see for yourself why this should be your new home! This property is being sold “as-is”.
